# IMPORTANT: Google OAuth requires a public domain. Use ngrok (recommended):
#   1. Sign up at https://dashboard.ngrok.com/signup
#   2. Install ngrok: https://ngrok.com/download
#   3. Run: ngrok config add-authtoken YOUR_TOKEN
#   4. Run: ngrok http 5050
#   5. Use the ngrok URL in Google Console and here:
#      - Application home page: https://abc123.ngrok-free.app
#      - Redirect URI: https://abc123.ngrok-free.app/api/auth/google/callback
#
# NOTE: localtunnel (loca.lt) does NOT work - Google rejects it!
#
